Release LTS.416.2 of June 24, 2024
New features
1. The requirement to fill in the reason for pausing the normative term can now be regulated by settings.
2. When configuring the connection of an
action
with an object type, a read-only mode lock indicator appeared.
3. After updating the platform and when first signing in, the application will show a modal window with a list of updates.
4. A collaborative work of users with comments was added. Answers to comments are displayed immediately for all users working with the document.
Changes and improvements
In dashboards, improvements in the possibility to algorithmically configure an attribute group style and name by the label,
Stabilizations in the Drill Down decryption;
Stabilizations in viewing attribute values of a business process run in the task profile;
Improvements in the System action and session audit;
Blocking the selection of system objects in a multiselect attribute can now be done without updating the page;
Filtering the registry settings when selecting algorithms can now be done by the object base type;
Stabilizations in selecting multiple registry objects;
Improvements in viewing data filtering window in the "Flat registry";
Stabilizations in underlying text when setting up the formatting style;
Improvements in selecting file classification when adding files;
Stabilizations in saving child objects in the "Receiver. Internal" ETL stage;
Optimizations in generating print forms with the printEDoc function;
Improvements in running the visibility algorithm for groups of tabs;
Itâ€™s now once again possible to name the
call room
without further editing;
Corrections in chat type names in the GreenData Messenger;
Improvements in pop-up notifications in the Messenger call service;
Improvements in the System audit and session end date display;
Corrections in the "Setting up external chats" type visual;
Optimizations in profile opening speed;
Optimizations in eDoc print form generation;
Optimizations in granting permissions;
A permission control by condition tree was added;
An HTML-injection vulnerability in monitoring tasks was fixed;
Updates in Swagger documentation;
An icon button was added to labels;
In
Kanban boards
, a possibility to create columns based on new values was added;
Improvements in the "Audit. Session" registry aimed at transferring data to event registration system with displaying the session end date;
In the
Exclusive mode
, the "Disable exclusive mode" button was hidden for all users except for those from the Administrative group;
Optimizations in "Setting external chats" visual type;
Viewing the "Color selection" attribute visual was enables;
Optimizations in insertions to the sys_type_attr_ref table;
Optimizations in task profiles opening;
Optimizations in viewing eDoc documents;
Updates in system buttons relative to normative terms;
Optimizations in opening eDoc documents and generating print forms;
Improvements in control elements and dashboard autofill algorithms;
Improvements in the parallel distribution of permissions.
